@startuml
' Golden template: synchronous request-response.
' Source scenario: a client makes one blocking call through an API and gets a value back.
' Solid arrow (->) is the synchronous call. Dashed arrow (-->) is the return.
' autoactivate on draws and balances the activation bars from the call and return arrows,
' so there is no manual activate or deactivate to leave unbalanced.
autonumber
autoactivate on
participant Client
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "Order Service" as Service
Client -> API : GET /orders/42
API -> Service : fetchOrder(42)
Service --> API : order
API --> Client : 200 order
@enduml
